  "text": "We describe the semantics of our cooperative kernels programming model (Sec. 3.1), use our motivating examples to discuss programmability (Sec. 3.2) and outline nonfunctional properties required by the model (Sec. 3.3). In the extended version of this paper we present a formal semantics, and discuss alternative semantic choices [CITATION_1] .",
